Section 13 A (3) which provides that \'91the parties to an intermediate or a large merger may not implement that merger until it has been approved\'85..\'92 must be read together with section 60(1) of the Act which provides that \'91If a merger is implemented in contravention of chapter 3, the Competition Tribunal may \'96 }
