that, \'91subject to this Part, where (a) a person, or two or more persons pursuant to an agreement or arrangement, proposed to acquire assets in the circumstances set out in sub-section 110 (2), to acquire shares in the circumstances set out in sub-section 110(3) to acquire an interest in a combination in the circumstances set out in sub-section 110(6) }
\par \pard\plain \s98{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sb0\sa120\cf0\kerning1\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\loch\f0\fs24\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
