The Canadian Act therefore envisages notification before completion of the merger and provides authority for the award of interim relief where a party seeks to complete or implement a\~   proposed merger.}
\par \pard\plain \s98{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\sb0\sa120\cf0\kerning1\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\loch\f0\fs24\lang7177{\rtlch \ltrch
